dct_title_s: Energy Web Atlas natural gas pipelines (USA), 2018
dct_description_sm: Lines representing natural gas pipelines in operation in the contiguous United States as of 2018. Data on pipeline types, capacities, operators, permits, and project scopes and descriptions is included.
